init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I say "I will have you removed from my shoulder and placed in a nice jar."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bee says "Your Majesty, I will do that but I must tell you that I am not a bee, I am a tiny fairy."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Yes, I am a fairy and I will grant you three wishes."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I say "I wish to be the most beautiful woman in the world."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The fairy says "Your wish is granted."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I say "I wish to be rich."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The fairy says "Your wish is granted."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I look at my shoulder and see a bee!

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I scream and the fairy disappears.
